msgid "Trigger Key"
msgstr "触发键"

#, c-format
msgid ""
"Press and hold this key to record. Release it to start recognition. Supports "
"regular keys, modifier keys, and modified key combinations. You can "
"configure multiple trigger keys. The config is stored at %s."
msgstr ""
"按住该键开始录音，松开后开始识别。支持普通按键、修饰键以及带修饰键的组合键。"
"可配置多个触发键。配置保存在 %s。"

msgid "Command Keys"
msgstr "命令键"

msgid ""
"Press and hold this key to record a voice command to operate on the selected "
"text. If there is no active selection, vinput falls back to the current "
"primary-selection clipboard text. Default is Right Control."
msgstr ""
"按住该键录制语音指令，将对当前选中的文本进行处理。如果没有选中文本，"
"vinput 将使用当前主选区剪贴板内容。默认是右 Ctrl。"

msgid "Postprocess Menu Keys"
msgstr "后处理选单键"

msgid ""
"Configure one or more keys to open the postprocess menu. The default is "
"Right Alt + Control."
msgstr "可配置多个按键，用于打开后处理选单。默认是右 Alt + Ctrl。"

msgid "ASR Menu Keys"
msgstr "语音识别菜单键"

msgid ""
"Configure one or more keys to open the ASR provider / model selection menu. "
"The default is F8."
msgstr "可配置多个按键，用于打开语音识别引擎 / 模型选择菜单。默认是 F8。"

msgid "Previous Page Keys"
msgstr "上一页键"

msgid ""
"Keys for paging to the previous page in the postprocess menu and the "
"postprocess candidate menu. Defaults to Page Up and keypad Page Up."
msgstr ""
"用于后处理选单和后处理候选菜单翻到上一页。默认是 Page Up 和小键盘 Page Up。"

msgid "Next Page Keys"
msgstr "下一页键"

msgid ""
"Keys for paging to the next page in the postprocess menu and the postprocess "
"candidate menu. Defaults to Page Down and keypad Page Down."
msgstr ""
"用于后处理选单和后处理候选菜单翻到下一页。默认是 Page Down 和小键盘 Page "
"Down。"

